                                      Simplebot

DESCRIPTION
-----------

Simplebot is a simple irc bot. It is not supposed to handle many servers,
basically it connects to QuakeNet.
Simplebot was made to consider commands as plugins, each module in src/module/
is supposed to handle a specific command.


INSTALLING / USAGE
------------------

Edit settings.py then run make from the root folder

AVAILABILITY
------------

  get source from github:
  http://github.com/fabriced/simplebot
  website... maybe someday


